{"tid":673100,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★郭思治：我就嚟攞綜援！","createTime":"2018-05-21T14:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T00:08:18.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"43bfdb75f91d1e4171a00e0c35f8850c92ed0116","tid":673100,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/220609_812749e1a307f38fd0a88b54bea55ff2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F220609_812749e1a307f38fd0a88b54bea55ff2.png&h=62ab55d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日股價暴瀉的民眾金融（279），今日再跌逾兩成至0.1元，其持股8%的中國全通（633），股價亦暴跌近六成至0.72。民眾證券董事總經理郭思治出席東方資本餐飲俱樂部發佈會時表示，最重要是公司運作正常。他續指，民眾金融仍然正常運作，民眾證券亦繼續做生意，「無受影響」。<br />\n<br />\n對於股價下跌，郭思治指難以估計，他表示，「公司一切都係正常，直到而家呢一分鐘，未來一段時期，個運作都仍然保持正常&hellip;&hellip;作為管理層來講，最重要就係公司運作正常，反而你買一隻股票贏定輸，我覺得唔係咁重要，喺我個角度來講。」<br />\n他續指，「如果你以今日收市價1毫子，如果你一路揸落嚟，帳面上虧蝕好多」。他補充，細價股的投機性較重，「風險管理真係要做到足」，「總之買完之後唔對板，我都係減持或者止蝕」。<br />\n他表示，因為股價持續下跌，他作為保守的投資者，會嚴格執行風險管理。對於民眾金融及中國全通兩隻股份，他稱，現時並未持有該兩隻股，「我暫時兩隻都唔會揀住」。他續指，沽貨是在最近一週發生，「幾時沽我諗已經唔重要，總之都係輸錢」，虧損金額方面，他笑稱「都係少少錢啦，<span style=\"color: red;\">就嚟攞綜援</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180521/58221001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F58221001&d=QCkAzDZkjj3i0qnYFRiarUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=fc3b919f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180521%2F58221001&h=65df5001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180521/58221001</a>"},{"pid":"2958542bda075f1d7801aba6a95539d72feace69","tid":673100,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:09:56.000Z","msg":"best choice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4acc329bef806567d5d31df7aaa85d7515e50682","tid":673100,"uid":33174,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:16:04.000Z","msg":"出黎做健身狗都大把師奶埋身 隨時好撈過做金融狗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/221459_978aad44656884bf102f8b653242d2ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F221459_978aad44656884bf102f8b653242d2ae.png&h=7e07ab98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d8d26a86306eab91391689203800753e5694537","tid":673100,"uid":33263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:27:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95f0e11efa440f1da0ee66cd47b02cb29fb0cbf","tid":673100,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/164607_750ddbf3ac6d9374f8e9193aa94ad2a7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F164607_750ddbf3ac6d9374f8e9193aa94ad2a7.gif&h=e4784eb0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0f02a9889e2008a8e21287f4d408cf8d6ac4a04","tid":673100,"uid":136727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b95f0e11efa440f1da0ee66cd47b02cb29fb0cbf","tid":673100,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/12/164607_750ddbf3ac6d9374f8e9193aa94ad2a7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F12%2F164607_750ddbf3ac6d9374f8e9193aa94ad2a7.gif&h=e4784eb0&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:36:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkg